<A>__{heavy rain. a road next to a heavily guarded bunker facility. a canvas covered army truck blows a tire in the road. the driver gets out. inspects the tire.}
<L>__{interior army truck night}
<A>__{four marines in black suits dive through a hole in the truckbed floor into a manhole in the road.}
<L>__{exterior army weapons compound front gate night}
<A>__{three army m.p.s at the front guardhouse. general hummel pulls up in a suburban. the m.p.s immediately recognise him and stand more rigidly.}
